      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine is currently running but requires immediate attention due to significant mechanical issues, and the transmission is struggling with gear shifts. Cosmetically, the body shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust and interior damage, so please expect to invest in substantial repairs to make it roadworthy.",
